{"tid":318463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"據報內地擬半年內禁網民「翻牆」","createTime":"2017-07-12T05:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T00:55:03.000Z","uid":42764,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3b265963af262d4c432acd74a568a68a6af2520c","tid":318463,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:50:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=228054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D228054&d=824RU93fzWklzC%2BX%2F3vUCROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1d639f6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D228054&h=9f6c2a24\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=228054</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地當局據報計劃禁止互聯網用戶，在未來半年透過「翻牆」連結外國網站，外界憂慮內地新聞和言論自由可能進一步受限制。<br />\n<br />\n內地利用網絡「防火長城」限制民眾進入Google、facebook和Twitter等海外搜尋網站和社交網站。他們一般要通過俗稱VPN的虛擬私人網絡才可「翻牆」，進入境外的互聯網世界。<br />\n<br />\n不過，未來半年要瀏覽這些網站，難度可能會更高。<br />\n<br />\n彭博新聞引述消息報道，內地政府已要求三大國營電信公司，包括中國移動、中國聯通和中國電信在明年二月前，禁止個人用戶使用VPN，其中一間VPN服務供應商亦表示本月初已停止服務。<br />\n<br />\n至於境內企業可租用專線連結至國際網絡，但必須註冊，以備審查。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述美中貿易全國委員會副主席帕克指，相信互聯網個人用戶將首當其衝，又強調若企業內部VPN遭到切斷，可能會引發外國企業減少在內地投資，後果嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n由於VPN一直處於內地法律的灰色地帶，當局正致力堵塞「防火長城」的漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n工業和信息化部今年一月發布通知，禁止用戶未經電信主管部門批准，自行建立或租用VPN。重慶市亦在三月修訂規例，在當地使用「翻牆」工具瀏覽境外網站可能會被判罰款，甚至追究刑事責任。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，在中共十九大召開前內地加強互聯網管制，避免政治敏感內容在網上流傳。不過，外界憂慮持續收緊互聯網審查制度，意味內地新聞和言論自由可能會進一步受限制。"},{"pid":"05a25714c2e37f83a6806fd173238ba4086acd5d","tid":318463,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2111891b6d8c3fc6d80652c01a9c71c49e7482c7","tid":318463,"uid":42764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"好快就有啲咩外國勢力利用互聯網推行反中既新聞出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2310022f7b9c91aab96de41e426c35a60911ab","tid":318463,"uid":84081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"德政呀<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG幾時先BAN大陸IP呀 好撚多5毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647b0b06ff7dfb0b1d415d7de3b80c0fc6b90fc4","tid":318463,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b287dcc15c0af8421df258aad79aa5c27aced001","tid":318463,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"陰謀撚，會唔會北韓果度有杖打，費時被大陸人知道解放軍勁廢，早 o 的拉閘。"},{"pid":"60070ecdb32a1f1d5d7c1658682f2f990bb19f40","tid":318463,"uid":117556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德政呀<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG幾時先BAN大陸IP呀 好撚多5毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n殺波台咪五毛全死"},{"pid":"83b138a29e995b352ae3d786f15a2f177b970a2f","tid":318463,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:35:02.000Z","msg":"真係一件好事. 大陸D 痴線佬唔使周圍走."},{"pid":"f28f5c8173d41211e9cdb75a7f1f3f848faf427b","tid":318463,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"五毛自然有專用通道架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce5392d4ef7d87551e0708c2b19e1aa8edea573","tid":318463,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36db85d5d3b6f2aecd57e55f2996b6a8dd4e5106","tid":318463,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike"